    "Subcategory 1: DemandsAs part of the first subcategory, the \"Demands\" of ethics are viewed as potential barriers that can stand in the way of AIWeidener & Fischer JMIR AI XSL • FO RenderX technology and the technological progress of AI-based applications in medicine: I always find it a bit difficult to draw this line between these ethical demands and the limits that then really stand in the way of technology and progress.",
